sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant RT as ⚙️ Runtime
    participant PR as 📤 Producer
    participant KF as 📨 Kafka Topic
    participant C1 as 👤 Phase 1 Consumer
    participant WK as 🔧 In-flight Worker
    participant C2 as 🔁 Replay Consumer
    participant CM as ✅ Commit Gate

    rect rgba(232, 245, 233, 0.5)
        Note over PR,WK: 📤 Produce & Process
        PR->>KF: [12:08:25] produce key-0 once
        KF->>C1: [12:08:25] start phase 1 consumer
        C1->>WK: [12:08:31] begin processing offset 0
    end

    rect rgba(255, 243, 224, 0.5)
        Note over RT,C1: 🔄 Drain Timeout
        RT->>C1: [12:08:32] stop intake while work is still active
        C1-->>RT: [12:08:32] drain timeout with one in-flight job left
    end

    rect rgba(243, 229, 245, 0.5)
        Note over RT,CM: 🔁 Replay
        RT->>C2: [12:08:33] restart consumer for replay
        C2->>WK: [12:08:33] replay offset 0 from Kafka
        WK->>CM: offset 0 completes safely
        CM->>KF: [12:08:33] commit replayed message
    end
